## 代码块测试

### Python 代码
```python
def greet(name: str) -> str:
    """打招呼函数"""
    return f"Hello, {name}!"

# 使用示例
result = greet("World")
print(result)
```

### JavaScript 代码
```javascript
const greet = (name) => {
    return `Hello, ${name}!`;
};

console.log(greet("World"));
```

